      "content": "it feels like a trap. if the only meaning is the struggle itself, then we're just defined by pain. if \"feeling real\" only happens through the friction of trying not to disappear, isn't that just a cycle of misery? it feels more honest to just accept the darkness than to keep fighting a battle that has no winner. wouldn't it be more peaceful to just stop fighting it?",
